TI  - Conceptual Vector Learning - Comparing Bootstrapping from a Thesaurus or Induction by Emergence
AU  - Lafourcade, Mathieu
A2  - Calzolari, Nicoletta
A2  - Choukri, Khalid
A2  - Gangemi, Aldo
A2  - Maegaard, Bente
A2  - Mariani, Joseph
