TI  - Detecting Contact-Induced Semantic Shifts: What Can Embedding-Based Methods Do in Practice?
AU  - Miletic, Filip
AU  - Przewozny-Desriaux, Anne
AU  - Tanguy, Ludovic
A2  - Moens, Marie-Francine
A2  - Huang, Xuanjing
