TI  - “Am I Answering My Job Interview Questions Right?”: A NLP Approach to Predict Degree of Explanation in Job Interview Responses
AU  - Verrap, Raghu
AU  - Nirjhar, Ehsanul
AU  - Nenkova, Ani
