TI  - An Exploratory Study on Long Dialogue Summarization: What Works and What's Next
AU  - Zhang, Yusen
AU  - Ni, Ansong
AU  - Yu, Tao
AU  - Zhang, Rui
AU  - Zhu, Chenguang
AU  - Deb, Budhaditya
AU  - Celikyilmaz, Asli
